attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a table. He starts by inspecting all the pieces, then assembling the legs and attaching the middle shelf. Finally, he screws the whole thing together.

attributes.Transcription: We'll now assemble a bedside table from IKEA, so please go ahead.
